insert into photos (id, category, imgUrl, title, content, cTime, click) values(default, 1, '["http://106.54.61.253/photos/11.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/12.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/13.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/14.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/15.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/16.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/17.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/18.jpg"]', '冬天结冰的瀑布', '瀑布在地质学上叫跌水，即河水在流经断层、凹陷等地区时垂直地从高空跌落的现象。在河流存在的时段内，瀑布是一种暂时性的特征，它最终会消失。', '2019-10-14 13:12:58', 3);
