insert into photos (id, category, imgUrl, title, content, cTime, click) values(default, 6, '["http://106.54.61.253/photos/231.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/232.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/233.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/234.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/235.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/236.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/237.jpg", "http://106.54.61.253/photos/238.jpg"]', '正在钓鱼的男子', '钓鱼是捕捉鱼类的一种方法。钓鱼的主要工具有钓杆，鱼饵。钓杆一般由竹子或塑料轻而有力的杆状物质制成，钓杆和鱼饵用丝线联接。', '2019-10-14 13:12:58', 3);
